    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been absolute gold. It\u2019s been really well-taken care of and still drives like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway. It's got plenty of life left in it and is just looking for a new owner to hit the road with. Come take it for a spin, I just know you're going to love how it handles!",
