    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle has been meticulously maintained and serves as a prime example of a well-cared-for daily driver. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous finish, with only minor road wear that you would expect from careful use. Inside, the cabin is smoke-free and remarkably clean; the upholstery shows minimal wear, and all technological features\u2014from the infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control\u2014function flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and quietly, reflecting a consistent service history. We recently completed a full multi-point inspection, including an oil change and brake check, ensuring it\u2019s road-ready. While it isn't a showroom trailer queen, it is a robust, reliable, and aesthetically pleasing car that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
