      "description": "We are pleased to present this distinguished vehicle, a testament to refined engineering and consistent care. This model has been maintained to an exacting standard, ensuring both mechanical reliability and a sophisticated aesthetic presence. It offers a superior driving experience, characterized by smooth performance and a well-preserved interior. This offering represents a premier opportunity for the discerning buyer to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that perfectly balances performance with enduring value.",
      "price": 34800.0,
