    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really great shape and has been super well-loved, making it the perfect companion for your daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. It runs smoothly and still looks fantastic\u2014I'm sure you\u2019re going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out if you want to take it for a spin!",
