    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically robust E46 M3 powered by the high-revving S54B32 inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This example features a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including a comprehensive VANOS system overhaul and rear subframe reinforcement to ensure chassis rigidity under lateral load. The suspension geometry remains tight with updated bushings and dampers, providing the communicative feedback this platform is known for. While the exterior shows honest character from spirited use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and thermal efficiency. A visceral, analog performance machine optimized for the curves.",
